    <div class="post" id="post-615">
     <h2>
      <a href="/">
       mnmlst
      </a>
      :
      <b>
       scty, rmgnd
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Smtms I wndr f scty cld b vstly dffrnt, rdsgnd lmst frm scrtch.
      </p>
      <p>
       It stms frm my blf tht smwhr lng th ln, w llwd rslvs t b sdtrckd frm wht’s mprtnt — ppl — nd nstd hv pt prfts, crprtns, prdctvty, nd cnsmng t th frfrnt f vrythng w d.
      </p>
      <p>
       W’v bcm wrkrs fcsd n prdctvty, bcs w nd t rn  lvng, s tht w cn … by thngs (ncldng ntrtnmnt). Incldng  cr, whch s ndd t g t wrk nd t shp. W nd t snd r kds t schl, s w dn’t nd t wrry bt thm whn w wrk, nd s tht thy cn grw p t b gd wrkrs. W nd t by fst fd nd cnvnnc fd, bcs w’r t bsy r trd frm wrk t ck.
      </p>
      <p>
       W’v gttn ft, trd, sck, dp n dbt, dscnnctd frm r kds nd thr fmly mmbrs, dvrcd, sprtd frm r nghbrs. W’r plltng nd csng glbl wrmng, ll n th nm f mny nd wrk nd prfts nd byng. Ths sms brkn, t m.
      </p>
      <p>
       Bt wht’s  bttr wy f lvng? A scty rmgnd, blt rnd ppl nd  lv fr r nvrnmnt nd lvng nd wrkng nd plyng tgthr,  lv fr bng tsd nd plyng nd bng ctv,  lv fr dng thngs nd spndng tm wth ppl rthr thn fr byng thngs nd wrkng t spprt tht byng hbt.
      </p>
      <p>
       Wht wld sch  scty lk lk? I hstt t pt frth my vsn, bcs t shldn’t cm frm n prsn bt shld b rmgnd by vryn wh wll lv t. Hwvr, I’ll pt frth  smll slvr f sch  vsn, jst t gt th cnvrstn strtd.
       <span id="more-615">
       </span>
      </p>
      <h3>
       Th cr, jnkd
      </h3>
      <p>
       I’d strt by bnshng th cr. It’s sppsd t gv s frdm, bt w’r chnd t t nd ts xpnsv pymnts, mntnnc, rprs, fl, prkng, plltn, nd s n. I’d prfr th frdm t wlk, bk, nd tk gd mss trnst, nd t ply n th rds gn. W’d rclm th rds s pblc spcs fr th cmmnty, nd rdsgn lf s tht mst vrythng w nd (fd, wrk, schl, ply, strs, rstrnts, tc.) r wthn wlkng r bkng dstnc, nd mss trnst s vlbl fr vrythng ls.
      </p>
      <p>
       Tht mns w’d nd t stp cmmtng t wrk. I’d prps tht mny ppl cld wrk frm hm, thr s ntrprnrs nd smll bsnss ppl r tlcmmt r cllbrt nln. Cls t r hms, w’d ls nd mrktts fr fd nd tls nd whtnt, nd ppl wh mk clths nd fd nd bks nd ll tht knd f stff, nt t mntn rpr nd mntn vrythng n th cmmnty. W’d nd bldrs nd mscns nd ll f tht t, bt t cld b dn mch clsr t hm.
      </p>
      <h3>
       Schls, rsd
      </h3>
      <p>
       I’d ls bnsh th schl, t lst s w knw t: nstttns tht frc lrnng, tht hmgnz chldrn, tht tch thm t b rbtc wrkrs nstd f thnkrs, crtrs, ndpndnt lrnrs. Ths sn’t  crtcsm f tchrs (wh I thnk r snts), bt f th systm tslf. Kds r trnd ff t lrnng bcs thy’r frcd t g t schl fr 6-8 hrs  dy, st t dsks, nt tlk r ply wth thr clssmts xcpt t dsgntd tms, d wrk thy’r nt ntrstd n, mmrz thngs wtht thnkng mch … prtty mch wht thy’r xpctd t d fr mst f thr dlt lvs, nlss thy’r lcky ngh t brk t f ths thnkng.
      </p>
      <p>
       Wht’s bttr? I
       <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unschooling">
        nschl
       </a>
       my kds, nd I thnk ths s  mch mr hmn systm, nd bttr f yr gl s t gt th kds t ctlly lrn, t njy lrnng, t fgr t hw t d thngs thmslvs, t crt nd b slf-mtvtd … prtty mch wht I hp my kds wll d s dlts. Hw d w d ths? W hlp thm fnd thngs thy’r ntrstd n, nd try nt t frc thm t d nythng. Thy rd bks thy fnd ntrstng, wrk n prjcts tht r fn t thm, gt xctd bt thngs, mk thngs. Rvltnry, I knw, bt nt tht hrd nc y brk t f th schlng mndst. W’r stll lrnng hw t nschl, s r r kds, bt f t wrn’t  lrnng prcss, t wldn’t b wrthwhl.
      </p>
      <p>
       S kds cld b nschld n my rmgnd scty, lrnng frm thr prnts r sblngs r grndprnts, r n thr wn, r frm wrkng mmbrs n thr nghbrhd wh r dng thngs thy’r ntrstd n. Or w cld hv lrnng cntrs, whr kds g f thy’r ntrstd n lrnng bt rt r msc r wrtng r cmptrs r ckng r bldng r whtvr — thy wldn’t b frcd t g hr, bt wld b prvdd wth th rsrcs. Unschls, prvdd by th cmmnty, spplntng th cst f rnnng th ld-fshnd styl schls.
      </p>
      <h3>
       Shrng vs. cnsmrsm
      </h3>
      <p>
       I’d gt rd f sprmrkts nd hg grbsnsss nd fd flwn nd shppd frm thsnds f mls wy. Instd, w’d grw r wn fd, rght n r bckyrds, r n cmmnty grdns. W’d swp fds wth nghbrs — sm f my swt ptts fr sm f yr qn. I thnk mr ppl wld bcm vgtrn/vgn ths wy, bt t wldn’t b rqrd — f y wntd t rs yr wn nmls nd kll thm, y cld. Ths systm wld b hgly bttr fr th nvrnmnt, nd r hlth, nd wld rcnnct s wth r fd nd ntr. W’d t whl, nprcssd fds, ckd tstly. It wld tk mr tm, I’m sr, bt slw fd sn’t sch  bd thng, nd f dn rght, t wldn’t hv t b t tm cnsmng, spclly f vryn ptchd n.
      </p>
      <p>
       I’d d wy wth th crprtn, nd pt th cprtv n ts plc. Crprtns r s nhmn, s prft-drvn, s hrrbl fr mplys nd th nvrnmnt (n gnrl, wth xcptns). Cprtvs r wnd by th wrkrs, nd s bvsly trt th wrkrs wth mr hmnty. Thy’r ls lss lkly t rp th rth r dmg th cmmnty r cstmrs. Thy’r smply  wy fr ppl t wrk tgthr dmcrtclly nd cprtvly.
      </p>
      <p>
       I’d chng th cncpt f hsng, smhw. Rght nw, t’s hgly wstfl, wth ppl byng ggntc hms wth ll knds f spc thy dn’t nd, ndng ll knds f htng/clng s  rslt, nd frcng ppl t wrk lng hrs t py fr t. Instd, w cld hv smllr hms, blt wth th hlp f nghbrs (thnk Amsh brn-rsng), s w’d nd fr fwr rsrcs t bld thm nd fr lss dbt t wn thm. W mght vn hv cmmnty hms, f ppl flt lk t, thgh tht wldn’t b mndtry. Ths wld llw
       <a href="http://shareable.net">
        shrng f rsrcs
       </a>
       , nd wld rdc th cst f lvng fr vryn nvlvd.
      </p>
      <p>
       I’d hv
       <a href="http://mnmlist.com/on-owning-nothing/">
        lbrrs fr vrythng
       </a>
       . Jst s bk lbrrs r sprngng p, nd cr shrng s bcmng mr cmmn n cts, nd thr lbrrs lk
       <a href="http://shareable.net/blog/sharing-is-contagious">
        tl lbrrs
       </a>
       r cmng nt pblc cnscsnss, w cld hv lbrrs fr ny knd f rsrcs: cmptrs, clthng, frntr, vn hss. Ths wld mn thngs wld b fr chpr t s, s w’d b shrng thm, nd t wld mn fr lss wst s wll.
      </p>
      <p>
       I’d hv zr dvrtsng, nd cls t zr cnsmrsm. W’d dscrg ppl “shppng” nd pyng fr ntrtnmnt nd tryng t by mr nd mr jst t mprss thrs, nd nstd fcs n xprncs nd shrng nd dng thngs tgthr — rdng nd crtng nd gng tsd fr hks nd ckng tgthr nd grdnng tgthr nd bldng tgthr nd fxng thngs tgthr r bng ln … bt nt byng.
      </p>
      <p>
       Wrk, lvng, nd cmmnty nds cld b rmgnd t — prhps w’d frm vlntry tms t tk cr f dffrnt thngs. Fr xmpl, f prks r strts ndd t b clnd, w cld hv tms t d tht, nd vryn cld vlntr  crtn nmbr f hrs (nt frcd, bt y’d prbbly b mbrrssd f y ddn’t pll yr shr). Anythng cld b rgnzd ths wy, vlntrly nd dmcrtclly: wrkplcs, tchng, ckng, cr f yng chldrn, whtvr th cmmnty wntd. Ths wld tk clsr-knt cmmnts, bt I thnk tht wld b mr pssbl wtht crs nd wth ppl wlkng nd bkng, nd dng thngs tgthr sch s cmmnty grdns nd bldng nghbrs’ hss.
      </p>
      <h3>
       A dgtl wrld
      </h3>
      <p>
       I’d hv fr wrlss Intrnt fr th ntr cmmnty, s tht vryn cld cllbrt nd hv ccss t nfrmtn nd dctn. Onln sts cld b sd t rgnz th cmmnty nd pt frth prpsls nd bld cnsnss. Th wrlss wld b pd fr by vryn, nd cld b dn wth th mny w sv frm fd nd nt hvng t bld nfrstrctr fr crs nd s frth. W cld ls lmnt th nd fr  tlphn systm, nd I’d ls gt rd f cbl TV systms, whch wld hlp py fr fr wrlss.
      </p>
      <p>
       I’d lmnt ppr, fr th mst prt. It’s  wst f trs nd tks p  lt f spc n ffcs nd ppl’s hss, nd thn ftn bcms wst. Bks, mgzns, nwspprs, CDs,
       <span class="caps">
        DVD
       </span>
       s ll bcm dgtl (s thy r lrdy). Pprwrk bcms dgtl, nd fxs r klld tw dcds ftr thy shld hv bn klld. W lmnt prntrs nd sv mr mny. All w hv r lttl ntbks nd jrnls nd sktchpds fr ths wh lk t wrt nd drw n ppr.
      </p>
      <h3>
       Th rslts
      </h3>
      <p>
       Thnk bt ths: wth ths chngs, w’d hv mch smllr lvng xpnss, bcs hsng wld b ffrdbl, w wldn’t b pyng fr crs, fd wld b chpr, schl wld b fr, thr thngs wld b chp bcs w’d b sng lbrrs fr vrythng. W’d nt b cnsmrs, bt bldrs nd crtrs nd grwrs. And s, wth sch smll xpnss, w wld hv t wrk fr lss t rn  lvng.
      </p>
      <p>
       Imgn tht: lwr xpnss mns wrkng lss, whch mns mr fr tm t … d nythng y wnt. T spnd tm wth frnds, fmly, kds, nghbrs. T b ln. T crt, t cmmn wth ntr, t b fr. T
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net/2009/09/do-interesting-things/">
        d ntrstng thngs
       </a>
       . All f tht fr tm, fr frm bng  drn n scty, cld b  hg bnft, s ppl wld b hppr, hv bttr fmly lvs, wld crt mr ntrstng thngs, wld b lss lkly t cmmt crms, nd s n. I’m nt syng ths wld crt  tp, bt I thnk t wld hv  pstv ffct. W’d, f crs, b mch bttr fr th nvrnmnt nd mch bttr fr r hlth, r snty, r hppnss.
      </p>
      <h3>
       Bck t rlty
      </h3>
      <p>
       <span class="caps">
        OK,
       </span>
       s by nw y’r syng, “Yh rght, L. Kp drmng.” And I cknwldg ths s  drm, bt th cnvrstn nds t b strtd smwhr. On th nt f prctclty, w wldn’t nd t chng th ntr wrld, r th ntr cntry r cltr. Jst n cmmnty, nd t cld b  smll n —  cllg twn sch s Astn r Dvs r Egn, r  nghbrhd sch s Np (n
       <span class="caps">
        S.F.
       </span>
       ). Ths cmmnty cld rgnz tslf nd rmgn tslf, nd mk n chng t  tm twrds  mr pstv ftr.
      </p>
      <p>
       Ths cmmnty, I thnk, wld nspr thrs, nd thr cmmnts mght sn fllw, jst s
       <a href="http://www.theglobeandmail.com/life/article766908.ece">
        Bgt
       </a>
       hs nsprd mny thr plcs wth sm f ts prgrssv plcs. By shwng t cn b dn, nd shrng sm f wht thy lrnd, ths rly cmmnts wld pv th wy fr thrs t strt dwn ths rd.
      </p>
      <p>
       It’s  rd I’d lv t wlk dwn myslf. Bt dn’t lt m tll y wht t d: rmgn th ftr yrslf, nd jn th cnvrstn.
      </p>
      <p>
       —
      </p>
      <p>
